{"tid":374191,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度有樣學樣邊境修路 中國惱羞成怒","createTime":"2017-08-25T14:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T00:51:35.000Z","uid":62257,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ebc5a0e57224707c051f0176d868488b8576d2","tid":374191,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:32:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-08-25/95898\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2017-08-25%2F95898&d=RlaQ%2Fiq9qU2E4FC%2FJh44NYzu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=a629869b\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2017-08-25/95898</a><br />\n中國與印度繼續在洞朗對峙，不過印度決定仿效中國，修築1條從拉達克（Ladakh）經馬爾斯米克拉（Marsimik La）隘口到熱泉（Hot Spring）的道路。此舉引發中國氣得跳腳，直說印度自己打臉，完全忘了自己也是因為修路才挑起爭端的「肇事者」。<br />\n<br />\n《The India PRESS》日前報導，印度國務院通過建設道路案，將在1萬8634英尺高的馬薩米克拉隘口興建長32.9公里的道路，耗資120.58億盧比，完成後將可以讓印度安全部隊順利進入拉達克地區以東的偏遠地區。官員還透露，還有其他73條道路也在建設。<br />\n<br />\n不過這個消息傳到中國耳裡，聽了實在不是味道。中國外交部發言人華春瑩24日在例行記者會上痛批，印度內政部批准建設1條從馬爾斯米克拉到熱泉的公路，馬爾斯米克拉到班公湖西北端僅20公里，印度在該地區修路，無助和平與穩定，而印方在中印邊界相關問題上說一套做一套，是自己在打自己的臉，對緩和當前兩國邊境地區的局勢也沒有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n中國似乎忘了，因為該國在今年6月中旬於洞朗地區修築公路，引發不丹緊張，才向印度求援，之後印度派兵進駐洞朗地區，中、印兩國軍隊就此在該地區形成對峙局面至今。"},{"pid":"173a3f0c9c75aadbd94db3640ae7123dc53a5494","tid":374191,"uid":78968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"自打嘴巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a848b7fab5caa32824b2aed5ffe16aa018c0092b","tid":374191,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"大陸封鎖消息，完全唔會有人知<br />\n話知大陸佬塊面腫過豬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865413cbde0f1733515ebcbb34d04fcc2a2adb71","tid":374191,"uid":27146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:37:47.000Z","msg":"印度起路咪又係唔敢打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7965600601c85ccaf6edd2724a6ff1ab2889cf6","tid":374191,"uid":139993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:42:31.000Z","msg":"以彼之道還施彼身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a597c4e281c5b2494460ee941eacc8f8074469","tid":374191,"uid":139993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"中共仲唔激到爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1dca2221caf9af48b5eea2fd44d80c23bf5f79a","tid":374191,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T15:51:37.000Z","msg":"見解放軍咁抽得仲唔嚇死"},{"pid":"e8e7aafb77e8e6e8f558c673dda3de6c64049225","tid":374191,"uid":106544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-25T16:16:45.000Z","msg":"淨係識出口術,樓下個阿伯都勇武過你"},{"pid":"fa786af6d5cafcccefc723a7005bfa4363dc3fcf","tid":374191,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見解放軍咁抽得仲唔嚇死</blockquote><br />\n叫解放軍修路可以會暈低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043e62576eac6dd27e34118a10dc0fb622aefadf","tid":374191,"uid":130262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:48:32.000Z","msg":"人地印度內政關你撚事咩支那人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0949d040333d0725c6c23fd2e1f6d8b58e8763b1","tid":374191,"uid":77730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-26T00:51:35.000Z","msg":"Rap咗出嚟"}]}